No. 369. Benjamin C. Chouteau, Plaintiff in Error, v. William Klapmeyer. In error to the Supreme Court of the State of Kansas. April 2, 1906. Mr. L. F. Bird for .plaintiff in error. Mr. James K. Polk, Mr. Andrew Wilson .and Mr. Noel W. Barksdale for defendant in error.

Dismissed with costs, on . motion of counsel for plaintiff in error.
